                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-02-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 3, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s January 11, and January 20. Has option been extended? If so, to what
                    date? Telegraph present status of matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
